    "to extract keyframes is not always effective because no single descriptor surpasses the others in all video cases.",
    "The authors proposed a method for the weighted fusion of several descriptors, automatically estimating the weight of each descriptor.",
    "These weights reflect the relevance of each descriptor to a particular video shot.",
    "They are used to form a combined similarity matrix, which is then used as an input to a spectral clustering algorithm and, ultimately, to obtain keyframes.",
    "Numerical experiments using various videos have shown that this method is effective in summarizing video shots regardless of the characteristics of the visual content of the video."
